categories: Category:Jedi trainees of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Veneka was a senior Jedi Padawan who was enrolled in the Jedi Order's academy on Coruscant.

A Padawan of the Jedi Order, Veneka was trained in the ways of the Force. During the Clone Wars, Veneka was stationed at the Coruscant Jedi Temple. Shortly after the Battle of Kothlis and was joined by fellow Padawan Ahsoka Tano as part of Green Team in a competition arranged by Master Taria Damsin. The competition, taking place in the new Sublevel nineteen training dojo, ended in a tie. Veneka was one of the two members of Green Team to make it all the way through the dojo.
